<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>Wendell Warman</author>
<hymn_number>140</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 There's a song in my heart
 A song filled with praise
 A song I will sing
 All of my days

[V2]
 Birthed in your love
 A sweet melody
 Stirring deep within
 Like waves of the sea

[V3]
 Be the sky above so blue
 Or turned dark and grey
 The song still abides
 It never goes away

[V4]
 Washed in your blood
 Made white as snow
 Your redeeming love
 Is music to my soul

[V5]
 CHORUS
 And I will sing of the glory of your name
 I will sing praises to you
 And I will sing of the greatness of your love
 I will sing of the wonders you do
 I will sing forever Jesus of you</lyrics>
<title>There's a song</title>
</song>